sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend (OAuth Client)
    participant NA as Naver Auth Server
    participant NR as Naver Resource Server

    U->>B: "네이버 로그인" 클릭
    B->>BE: GET /oauth2/authorization/naver
    BE-->>B: 302 Redirect to Naver authorize URL + state

    B->>NA: GET /oauth2.0/authorize?...&state=...
    NA-->>B: 302 Redirect to /login/oauth2/code/naver?code=AUTH_CODE&state=...

    B->>BE: GET /login/oauth2/code/naver?code=AUTH_CODE&state=...
    Note over BE: Spring Security가 state 검증

    BE->>NA: POST /oauth2.0/token (code=AUTH_CODE)
    NA-->>BE: access_token

    BE->>NR: GET /v1/nid/me (Bearer access_token)
    NR-->>BE: user info

    Note over BE: 자체 1회용 EXCHANGE_CODE 생성
    BE-->>B: 302 Redirect to frontend callback URL?code=EXCHANGE_CODE

    B->>FE: Front callback page 진입
    FE->>BE: POST /auth/oauth2/exchange (EXCHANGE_CODE)
    BE-->>FE: access_token JSON + Set-Cookie(refresh token)

    FE->>BE: 이후 API 요청 (Authorization: Bearer access_token)
